/* 名片对外页 = 清新浅色 + 薄荷青；干净可信（发给客户/HR 的脸）。付费弹层保持白底。 */
.page { padding: 36rpx 32rpx 120rpx; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; background: #fbfcfb; }

.card { background: #fff; border-radius: 28rpx; border: 1rpx solid #ecefec; box-shadow: 0 2rpx 8rpx rgba(20, 40, 30, 0.04); }
.muted { color: #8a9a93; }

/* hero */
.hero { margin-bottom: 22rpx; padding: 36rpx 32rpx; }
.hero .amb-layer { display: none; }
.hero-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24rpx; }
.hero-ava { flex: 0 0 auto; width: 120rpx; height: 120rpx; border-radius: 32rpx; background: #e8f5ef; }
.hero-ava-ph { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.hero-ava-ph .ic { font-size: 56rpx; color: #18b690; }
.hero-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
.name { font-size: 38rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #16241e; letter-spacing: -0.5rpx; }
.title-text { font-size: 26rpx; margin-top: 8rpx; color: #8a9a93; }
.city { font-size: 24rpx; margin-top: 4rpx; color: #aab4af; }

.one-liner { margin-top: 26rpx; font-size: 32rpx; font-weight: 500; color: #16241e; line-height: 1.55; }
.tags { margin-top: 20rpx; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14rpx; }
.tag { background: #e8f5ef; color: #0c5a48; font-size: 24rpx; padding: 8rpx 20rpx; border-radius: 999rpx; }

.section { margin-bottom: 22rpx; padding: 32rpx; }
.section-title { font-size: 28rpx; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16rpx; color: #16241e; }
.full-intro { font-size: 28rpx; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a5a53; white-space: pre-wrap; }

.stats { display: flex; padding: 28rpx 0; }
.stat { flex: 1; text-align: center; position: relative; }
.stat::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 10rpx; bottom: 10rpx; width: 1rpx; background: #f0f2f0; }
.stat:last-child::after { display: none; }
.stat-num { font-size: 44rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #16241e; }
.stat-label { font-size: 22rpx; margin-top: 6rpx; color: #9aa8a1; }

.income-card { padding: 28rpx 32rpx; margin-bottom: 22rpx; }
.income-row { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 16rpx; }
.income-num { font-size: 48rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #16241e; }
.income-label { font-size: 24rpx; color: #8a9a93; }
.income-sub { font-size: 22rpx; margin-top: 10rpx; color: #8a9a93; }

.actions { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18rpx; margin-top: 32rpx; }
.btn-accent { background: #18b690; color: #fff; border-radius: 999rpx; font-size: 30rpx; font-weight: 500; padding: 26rpx 0; }
.btn-accent::after { border: none; }
.btn-ghost { background: #fff; color: #2a3a33; border: 1rpx solid #dfe5e1; border-radius: 999rpx; font-size: 29rpx; padding: 26rpx 0; }
.btn-ghost::after { border: none; }

.empty { text-align: center; padding-top: 240rpx; color: #aab4af; }
.brand-foot { text-align: center; font-size: 24rpx; padding: 32rpx 0 16rpx; color: #8a9a93; }
.trust-badge { font-size: 24rpx; color: #2f8c72; margin: -6rpx 0 16rpx; }

/* fresh 庆祝卡：薄荷青浅底 */
.fresh-card { padding: 32rpx; text-align: center; background: #e6f5ee; border: 1rpx solid rgba(24, 182, 144, 0.3); border-radius: 28rpx; margin-bottom: 22rpx; }
.fresh-title { font-size: 36rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #0c3a2e; }
.fresh-sub { font-size: 26rpx; margin: 12rpx 0 8rpx; color: #4a7a6c; }
.fresh-starters { margin-bottom: 20rpx; }
.fresh-starter { font-size: 26rpx; color: #2f6f5c; line-height: 1.9; }
.fresh-actions { display: flex; gap: 16rpx; }
.fresh-btn { flex: 1; }
.fresh-notify { margin-top: 16rpx; padding: 18rpx 24rpx; border-radius: 16rpx; text-align: center; font-size: 24rpx; color: #0f766e; background: #d6efe4; }
.fresh-notify.done { color: #6a9a8c; background: #e6f5ee; }

/* 付费弹层：白底（成交时刻干净可信） */
.mask { position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; }
.tip-sheet { width: 100%; background: #fff; border-radius: 32rpx 32rpx 0 0; padding: 40rpx 32rpx calc(40rpx + env(safe-area-inset-bottom)); }
.tip-title { font-size: 34rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #16241e; }
.tip-sub { font-size: 24rpx; margin-top: 8rpx; color: #8a9a93; }
.tip-amounts { display: flex; gap: 20rpx; margin: 32rpx 0; }
.tip-amount { flex: 1; text-align: center; padding: 28rpx 0; background: #f3f6f4; border-radius: 16rpx; font-size: 32rpx; font-weight: 600; color: #16241e; border: 2rpx solid transparent; }
.tip-amount.active { border-color: #18b690; background: #fff; }
.tip-msg { background: #f3f6f4; border-radius: 16rpx; padding: 24rpx; font-size: 28rpx; margin-bottom: 32rpx; color: #16241e; }
.tip-pay { margin-top: 8rpx; background: #18b690; color: #fff; }
.tip-pay::after { border: none; }
